               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400203-name-1210" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-1210" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-1210" type="surname" value="LACK"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-1210" type="given" value="MARIA ROWE"></interp>MARIA ROWE LACK</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a widow, and live in Tooley-street, I keep a tobacconist's-shop—on the 3rd of February I was coming out of the back-kitchen into the shop—I saw the prisoner reaching over the counter to the window where the tobacco and cigars were—he ran away—I fol<lb></lb>lowed him a short distance, and raised an alarm—I missed a roll of to<lb></lb>bacco from the window, weighing 2 1/2lbs., which I had seen not three minutes before I saw him take it—this is it—(<hi rend="italic">looking at it</hi>)—I can swear to it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400203-name-1211" type="witnessName">
