                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-1211" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES NICHOLLS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. Byles. Last Monday; about three o'clock in the afternoon, I was at our door, and heard a cry of "Stop thief"—I ran and stopped the prisoner, with this tobacco in his hand.</p>
